Changelog
=========

1.2.3 - 2025-05-07
------------------

- Leap year error is fixed
- end_date parameter is added
- arrow removed from dependencies

1.2.2 - 2024-11-05
------------------

- Units correction: 1) Renamed output attribute P[MW] -> E[MWh]. 2) New P[MW] attribute <- repeat the last hourly P[MW] for a time interval less or equal than one hour, take the average value of the hourly P[MW] for the time interval exceeding one hour
- New caching component used
- Tests were added

1.2.1 - 2024-10-04
------------------

- PVGIS API update
- Minor changes

1.2 - 2024-02-13
------------------

- Control signal and gen_neg parameter are added
- Minor changes

1.0 - 2024-01-11
------------------

- Restructured as a mosaik component
- Readme and examples added
- Initial release of version implemented by Danila Valko
